name: ellow
description: Yellow is a meme token launched on bnbchain, which is launched from fourmeme. $Y token has no utility so far. It aims to use yellow elements for secondary creation and viral spread. Since Binance's elements are mainly yellow, the goal of $Y is to build a community that likes yellow. By sharing memes and art related to yellow,brings Y token holders together closely. This is a PVE social experiment and also a performance art, to see whether the community can make a project better and whether it can make a yellow circle bigger and bigger.
